payload.text: How can BestBuy maximize its profits and revenue in a high tarrif environment?

metadata.objective: Tarrifs from China are over 55% on electronics. Vietnam taffics are about 20%. Mexico tarrifs are over 10%. Tarrifs are widespread and  BestBuy needs to find ways to maximize profits and revenue in this environment. Consider supply chain, pricing, and customer engagement strategies.
